Quickstrike:





Quickstrike was a little stiff when he woke up. He was just a bundle of bot 
underneath the blanket. He shook his head and stretched his legs out. He 
didn't realize it at first, but he almost kicked Stingtra. She sat up, 
looking at her.

"Morning," he said to her half unconsciously.

He striped the blanket off of himself and looked at the interior of the 
cave. It was daylight, so that meant there was more planing (if Megatron 
wanted it that way)to do. He saw Dark Mouse at the console. He need to talk 
to her. The new flier, Terrorsaur was just taking off from his perch that 
was a mound of stalactmite. He stood up and walked towards Dark Mouse. He 
stood behind her and put his cobra hand on her shoulder.

"Ah want ya show me how this computer works." he said to her.
